name: Schandis Restaurant

reviews.review_text:
The Persian non veg platter was a delight. Chicken and lamp pieces perfectly marinated and cooked, along with saffron rice and mast o khiar which was the perfect dip.
The veg platter was also good but the dessert was something that I would want to go back again for.. baghlava and knafeh

A hidden treasure for anyone seeking authentic Persian cuisine. The seafood is fresh, and the flavors are perfectly balanced. The platters are absolutely amazing and we gorged ourselves on their Knafeh and Baklawa even after finishing two entire platters. The service is warm and attentive. Definitely worth the visit if you're in the area.

I absolutely fell in love with Persian food! We tried the veg mezze platter and chicken kubedeh, and both were delicious. Each dish on the mezze platter had its own unique taste, which made every bite exciting (especially when paired with zattar naan). The falafel were the best I've ever had and The chicken kubedeh was juicy and full of flavor!! I would definitely recommend trying these dishes!

description:
### Review of Schandis Restaurant: A Culinary Gem in Caranzalem

Nestled in the scenic neighborhood of Caranzalem, **Schandis Restaurant** shines with an impressive rating of **4.4** stars from **720 reviews**, making it a noteworthy spot for both locals and tourists alike. Renowned for its enticing **Persian cuisine**, this establishment is a must-visit for food enthusiasts, especially those craving fresh seafood, delectable **biryani**, inviting **naan**, and a relaxed atmosphere perfect for enjoying a **hookah**.

#### Ambiance & Design

Schandis Restaurant exudes a warm and inviting ambiance that complements its rich culinary offerings. Its décor is a blend of modern chic and traditional Persian elements, creating a cozy space where diners can truly unwind. Dim yet thoughtful lighting casts an inviting glow over the dining area, accentuating the vibrant colors of the dishes served. Customers have appreciated the subdued music that plays in the background, enhancing the dining experience without overwhelming conversation. The layout invites patrons to enjoy their meals while soaking in the beach vibes synonymous with Goa’s coastal charm, as suggested by the recurrent mention of the **beach** in customer tags.

#### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Schandis is a celebration of Persian flavors, offering a variety of impressive dishes that cater to all palates. Signature highlights include the **Persian non-veg platter**, featuring perfectly marinated chicken and lamb that come alive with spices, paired harmoniously with aromatic **saffron rice** and a refreshing **mast o khiar** dip. Vegetarian options such as the **veg mezze platter** also steal the spotlight, presenting diners with an array of thoughtfully crafted items—each offering its own unique taste experience supported by beloved **zattar naan**. Many have praised the indulgent desserts as well, particularly the **Baklava** and **Knafeh**, which entice guests to return even after their main courses.

For those with dietary preferences, Schandis does offer a number of vegetarian dishes, ensuring everyone can find something delightful on the menu.

#### Customer Experience & Service

Patrons often commend the attentive and warm service provided by the staff at Schandis. The restaurant’s team strives to create a welcoming environment, contributing to the restaurant's popularity among guests. Visitors have mentioned that the service is efficient, striking a nice balance between promptness and hospitality. Whether securing a reservation or simply walking in, guests report a seamless dining experience, further enriched by the staff's genuine enthusiasm for Persian cuisine.

#### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Schandis restaurant is palpable, with diners frequently taking to social media to share their culinary experiences. The overwhelmingly positive sentiments emphasize the restaurant not only as a hotspot for exquisite Persian dishes but also as a hospitable dining destination. While no specific critic ratings or awards were noted, the sheer volume of enthusiastic reviews serves as a testament to its quality and appeal.

#### Utilizing Visual Content

The vibrant culinary presentations are perfectly captured in customer-shared images, showcasing the stunning allure of dishes like the non-veg and veg platters, making your taste buds tingle with anticipation. The sumptuous spread of intricate plates adorned with fresh herbs and spices reflects the restaurant's attention to detail and commitment to a quality dining experience. You'll want to scroll through the beautiful representation of **Baklava** and **Knafeh**, which beckon dessert lovers in every photo.

### Conclusion

In conclusion, Schandis Restaurant is a hidden treasure for anyone looking to dive into the rich world of **Persian cuisine**. With its inviting atmosphere, skilled culinary offerings, and attentive service, it is undoubtedly a go-to destination in Caranzalem. Whether you’re a local or a traveler, Schandis is well worth a visit, offering a delightful fusion of flavors that will leave a lasting impression.
